item.title: [HBASE-15728] Add remaining per-table region / store / flush / compaction related metrics
item.description:
Continuing on the work for per-table metrics, HBASE-15518 and HBASE-15671.

We need to add some remaining metrics at the per-table level, so that we will have the same metrics reported at the per-regionserver, per-region and per-table levels.

After this patch, most of the metrics at the RS and all of the per-region level are also reported at the per-table level.
item.summary: Add remaining per-table region / store / flush / compaction related metrics

status.description: The issue is open and ready for the assignee to start work on it.
